Articles.Content:
The last word in luxury, if luxury ever existed! These broken devices made from parts found by the old JebCo. factory should be able to get you from A to B, but nothing beyond that! Take a look. Please? Anybody?

MODEL F "PRANCER"

The Prancer is a light, urban vehicle, without the light, urban part! This peppy little guy will have you zipping around corners with it's innovative 4wd, 4ws (four wheel drive/steering) system! It's wide body will allow you to take the sharpest of turns, and make you look like the sharpest of Kerbs. (Warning: can not take sharp turns)

MODEL X "GROVELER"

Military specs without the Military Price! The Groveler is a high-manuverability, high-stregnth and high-injury-rating vehicle! This version is available to the public, holding 6 seats and airdrop-ability! Comes with free cookie.
